	<strong>User Interface Designer</strong></p>
<p>
	At DeskPRO we consider the user experience of our product a significant competitive advantage. Design is not an afterthought but is baked into the very foundations of the product.</p>
<p>
	We are looking for a talented UI designer who will lead our design process. You will be able to take ideas from concept (and mockup)&nbsp; to PSD and finally to completed XHTML/CSS/Images for the backend developers to work with.</p>
<p>
