<ul>
	<li>
		Software user interface design experience</li>
	<li>
		Capable of creating stunning graphics, icons and buttons</li>
	<li>
		Expert XHTML/CSS</li>
	<li>
		A dedication to getting the details just right</li>
	<li>
		You love sites like dribbble and littlebigdetails.</li>
	<li>
		You have a portfolio of work to show us</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Bonus Points</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Basic use of javascript (jQuery)</li>
	<li>
		Familiarity with version control software</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>What we Offer:</strong></p>
<ul>
